# id: ZooKeeperProducer -> private OperationResult synchronouslySetData(ProductionContext ctx) throws Exception
commentText: Tries to set the data first and if a no node error is received then an_attempt will be made to create it instead.
codeText: private OperationResult synchronouslySetData(ProductionContext ctx) throws Exception {__        SetDataOperation setData = new SetDataOperation(ctx.connection, ctx.node, ctx.payload)__        setData.setVersion(ctx.version)___        OperationResult result = setData.get()___        if (!result.isOk() && configuration.isCreate() && result.failedDueTo(Code.NONODE)) {_            log.warn(format("Node '%s' did not exist, creating it.", ctx.node))__            result = createNode(ctx)__        }_        return result__    }
